<div id="New-Player">
  <h2 class="fs-5">New Player</h2>
  <div class="p-3 shadow-container intro-new-player mb-4">
    <div>
      <h3 class="fs-5 header">Introduction</h3>
      <p>First and foremost, this section is made both for new players and for more in depth explanations on what you have seen above, to answer common questions, teach you and much more. <span class="focus">If you like learning, this is your place.</span></p>
      <p><span class="focus-tag">Skip</span> If you don't care about the basics, and you want to jump right into gameplay experience, start from the section number 4.</p>
    </div>
    <section class="selection">
      <!-- Basics -->
      <article class="article">
        <a href="#Basics-Section" class="icon"> <i class="fa-solid fa-1"></i></a>
        <div class="content"> 
          <h4 class="fs-5 header">Basics</h4>
          <p>Starting point if you have no experience with the game at all. You will also learn some useful tricks.</p>
          <h5 class="fs-6 header">Content table:</h5>
          <div class="content-table">
            <a class="content-link" href="#Tutorial">Tutorial</a>
            <a class="content-link" href="#Eden-Academy">Eden Academy</a>
