            <a class="content-link" href="#Learning-DP">Learning Divine Pride</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <!-- Fundamentals -->
      <article class="article">
        <a href="#Fundamentals-Section" class="icon"> <i class="fa-solid fa-2"></i></a>
        <div class="content"> 
          <h4 class="fs-5 header">Fundamentals</h4>
          <p>Ideal place if you already know something but you're looking to learn some of the basics, like how to get by, what to look out for, what are your goals, etc.</p>
