      <article class="article">
        <a href="" class="icon"> <i class="fa-solid fa-4"></i></a>
        <div class="content"> 
          <h4 class="fs-5 header">Earlygame</h4>
          <p>This ranges from level 0 to 100. From <span class="focus">Swordman</span> to <span class="focus">Lord Knight</span>.</p>
          <h5 class="fs-6 header">Content table:</h5>
          <div class="content-table">
            <a href="#Earlygame-Stats" class="content-link">Stats</a>
